summary: Standalone worker integration tests
description: |
    Tests the pull model with pre-built container images. A standalone
    worker claims items via the workqueue HTTP API, processes them
    locally, and reports completion. Dispatcher runs in scale-only mode.
test: bash tests/container/run-standalone.sh
duration: 10m
require:
    - docker
    - docker-compose
    - curl
    - python3
framework: shell
